# ============================================
# NOTES FOR RUBY WINGS v5.2.1:
# ============================================
#
# 1. LINE ENDINGS:
#    - All Python, shell, config files use LF (Unix)
#    - Windows batch files use CRLF
#    - Binary files are never converted
#
# 2. EXPORT-IGNORE:
#    - Test files excluded from archives
#    - Dev configs excluded
#    - IDE settings excluded
#
# 3. BINARY HANDLING:
#    - FAISS indexes are binary
#    - Numpy files (.npz, .npy) are binary
#    - All ML model files are binary
#
# 4. CROSS-PLATFORM:
#    - Works on Windows, macOS, Linux
#    - Shell scripts always have LF
#    - Proper handling of text vs binary
#
# 5. GIT OPERATIONS:
#    - Clean diffs for text files
#    - Binary files show as "binary"
#    - Lock files use binary merge
#
# ============================================